== Limited time events ==

''Main article: [[Events/Limited-time events]]''

These events happen for a set period of time, depending on the day, holiday and what's in the news.

== Boosts ==

'''Boosts''' are special events where [[Stats]] can be improved just by doing one activity when a boost is available. The player may choose the first option and boost the stat or the second option to decline the opportunity and not get boosted. Unless the player has [[Bitizenship]], they must watch an ad every few boosts. Children can get boosts, but their boost events are different from that of adults.

